thread.title: Michelle

author: Michelle
title: Michelle
text: This is the first time I have used Airtasker. I found the tender / approval process to be very easy to use and stress free which allowed me to focus on the main task of packing up. The movers were professional, friendly, obliging and very competent. I liked being able to communicate directly with the service providers via Airtasker during the tender process and leading up to the move. It made me feel like I was in control of a very personalised service from start to finish.
